attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Coastal and Lakes & Mountains Realty

data.description: Great start to affordable homeownership here! You can own this whole duplex for less than the cost of renting an apartment: income from one side pays about half of the monthly payment! Each side has two bedrooms / one bath. The furnace and hot water heaters are located in the partial basement. Town water and sewer. Unit 23 is occupied, month to month.  Unit 25 has fresh paint and is ready to occupy. First time buyers: see if you qualify for Maine Housing financing, with rates just under 6% (3/2024). Investors: strong rental history in the neighborhood. Within walking distance to the shipyard.
